1.0.name: wordpress/bangla-ajax-calender
1.0.description:
This plugin is discontinued. Please see: http://wordpress.org/extend/plugins/bangla-ajax-calendar/

Displays a widget with bilingual post calendar. Gives a calendar with both Bongabdo and Gregorian Calendar. The Bangla Date plugin (Version 1.2) is required with this.
